Write a program to calculate the sum of digits of a given number.

Input Format

A single integer N

Constraints

0 ≤ N ≤ 10⁹

Output Format

Print the sum of digits.

Sample Input 0

123
Sample Output 0

6
Sample Input 1

4567
Sample Output 1

22

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#include <stdio.h>
#include <string.h>
#include <math.h>
#include <stdlib.h>

int main() {

    int n,sum=0;
    scanf("%d",&n);
    while(n>0){
        int digit=n%10;
        sum+=digit;
        n/=10;
    }   
    printf("%d",sum);
    return 0;
}


